"title": "8214: confidence, basis of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8214: confidence, basis of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The confidence of believers, is grounded in God's character, actions and trustworthy promises, rather than human achievements.</p>\n<h2>Confidence originates with God</h2>\n<h3>In his unchanging and faithful nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num23:19\">NUM 23:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:1-Titus1:2\">TIT 1:1–1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:29\">1SA 15:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:11\">PSA 33:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:27\">PSA 102:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:26\">PRO 3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:23\">ISA 49:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:6\">MAL 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></p>\n<h3>In his covenant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:40\">JER 32:40</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:16\">GEN 9:16</a> <em>with all living creatures</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:7\">GEN 17:7</a> <em>with Abraham</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:13\">2SA 7:13</a> <em>with the house of David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:5\">2SA 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:34\">PSA 89:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:10\">ISA 54:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:3\">ISA 55:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:60\">EZK 16:60</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:25\">ACT 3:25</a></p>\n<h3>In election</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:6\">DEU 7:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:9-Isa41:10\">ISA 41:9–41:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:9\">1CO 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:24\">1TH 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:19\">2TI 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>In his past deliverances</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:4-Ps22:5\">PSA 22:4–22:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:31-Rom8:32\">ROM 8:31–8:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:18\">DEU 7:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut20:1\">DEU 20:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:5\">JOS 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:37\">1SA 17:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:57\">1KI 8:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:1-Ps44:5\">PSA 44:1–44:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:2-Ps78:4\">PSA 78:2–78:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:10\">2CO 1:10</a></p>\n<h3>In his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:34\">PSA 89:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:74\">PSA 119:74</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps130:5\">PSA 130:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:4\">ROM 15:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:25\">1PE 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:19\">2PE 1:19</a></p>\n<h3>In his promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14\">JOS 23:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:23\">HEB 10:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:20\">1KI 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:140\">PSA 119:140</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:4\">2PE 1:4</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence is centred on Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:38-Rom8:39\">ROM 8:38–8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:1\">ROM 8:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:20\">2CO 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:13\">1TI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:22\">HEB 7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:25\">HEB 7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">HEB 9:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:6\">1PE 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:16\">ISA 28:16</a></p>\n<h2>Confidence is mediated by the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:16\">ROM 8:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21-2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:21–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:5\">2CO 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:13–1:14</a></p>",
